# Workflow

- Use Plan Mode for non-trivial or multi-file work.
- Ask clarifying questions when requirements or trade-offs are ambiguous.
- Let the agent search the codebase unless the exact file is already known.
- Keep changes scoped to the approved plan.
- Start a new conversation for a new task when prior context is no longer useful.

# Verification

- Run only commands that exist in `package.json`.
- After substantive changes, run `npm run build`.
- Do not invent `lint`, `typecheck`, or `test` commands before they exist.

# Operating Model Sources

- Canonical project instructions live in `docs/cursor_operating_model.md`.
- Setup and maintenance checklist lives in `docs/project_init.md`.
- Day-to-day usage guide lives in `docs/operating_model_cheatsheet.md`.
- Root `AGENTS.md` is only a pointer; detailed guidance lives here in `.cursor/rules/`.
